<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Optimize imports</b></p><p>You can delete import statements for all unused packages within a file. Press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:OptimizeImports;</span> (<span class="control">Code | Optimize Imports</span>) or <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:ShowIntentionActions;</span> (when the caret is at the import statement), and then select <span class="control">Optimize Imports</span>.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij_tod_optimize_imports.png" alt="Optimize imports" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>